data.description: 2.75 VA ASSUMPTION AVAILABLE!!! Welcome to a charming 4 bedroom 3 bathroom home nestled in New Braunfels, TX. This beautiful home showcases an open-concept layout, a bonus room upstairs, spacious closets, updated cabinetry and baseboards! The backyard features a covered patio and a large yard for activities and entertaining! Conveniently located, this home offers easy access to schools, parks, and shopping centers. Schedule a showing today and come see why 432 Sand Cherry is the perfect place to call home!
